/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ffa%2F7d%2Fc4d3ccfb4f77a6211942ae04792b%2Fgettyimages-537931570.jpg 1600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3000x2000+0+0/resize/1800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ffa%2F7d%2Fc4d3ccfb4f77a6211942ae04792b%2Fgettyimages-537931570.jpg 1800w" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3000x2000+0+0/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ffa%2F7d%2Fc4d3ccfb4f77a6211942ae04792b%2Fgettyimages-537931570.jpg" sizes="(min-width: 1025px) 650px, calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/jpeg" /&gt;             &lt;img src="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3000x2000+0+0/resize/1100/quality/50/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ffa%2F7d%2Fc4d3ccfb4f77a6211942ae04792b%2Fgettyimages-537931570.jpg" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3000x2000+0+0/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ffa%2F7d%2Fc4d3ccfb4f77a6211942ae04792b%2Fgettyimages-537931570.jpg" class="img" alt="Newly-minted graduates are also encountering some storm clouds in the job market." loading="lazy" /&gt;         &lt;/picture&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="credit-caption"&gt;     &lt;div class="caption-wrap"&gt;         &lt;div class="caption" aria-label="Image caption"&gt;             &lt;p&gt;                 Newly-minted graduates are also encountering some storm clouds in the job market.                 &lt;b class="credit" aria-label="Image credit"&gt;                                          Spencer Platt/Getty Images                                      &lt;/b&gt;                 &lt;b class="hide-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;             &lt;/p&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;               &lt;b class="toggle-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;     &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;p&gt;The U.S. unemployment rate is low, but few businesses are adding jobs, and most people who already have jobs are hesitant to give them up. This situation has made it hard for new college grads to start their careers. Economists suggest that this pattern is common among new graduates, making it one of the most challenging job markets they've faced in years, excluding the pandemic period. Alongside job cuts by the federal government, tech companies and consulting firms are also reducing their workforce after a phase of rapid growth. Employers are also generally cautious about hiring due to uncertain trade and tax policies. Here's what else is &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2025/07/13/nx-s1-5462807/college-graduates-jobs-employment-unemployment" target="_blank"&gt;currently impacting the job market for recent graduates&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;h3 class="edTag"&gt;3 things to know before you go&lt;/h3&gt;   &lt;div id="resg-s1-78000" class="bucketwrap image large"&gt;             &lt;div     class="imagewrap has-source-dimensions"     data-crop-type=""     style="         --source-width: 5860;         --source-height: 3906;     " &gt;         &lt;picture&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5860x3906+0+0/resize/400/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F51%2Fcd%2F3202e2db44898d34cc092a70da70%2Fgettyimages-2225436610.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5860x3906+0+0/resize/600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F51%2Fcd%2F3202e2db44898d34cc092a70da70%2Fgettyimages-2225436610.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5860x3906+0+0/resize/800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F51%2Fcd%2F3202e2db44898d34cc092a70da70%2Fgettyimages-2225436610.jpg 800w, 