      <title>Trump to meet with NATO over Russia-Ukraine war. And, a list of Trump's tariff letters</title>
      <author>Brittney Melton</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/07/14/g-s1-77455/up-first-newsletter-trump-tariffs-european-union-nato-russia-ukraine-texas-floods</link>
