      <title>Trump to assess Texas flood damage today. And, DOGE has access to farmers' payments</title>
      <author>Brittney Melton</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/07/11/g-s1-77166/up-first-newsletter-texas-floods-trump-doge-usda-brazil-tariffs</link>
