      <title>How to help Texas flood survivors. And, health organizations sue RFK Jr.</title>
      <author>Brittney Melton</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/07/08/g-s1-76507/up-first-newsletter-texas-flooding-tariffs-robert-kennedy-lawsuit</link>
